The Spanish side is commonly referred to as La Roja  (  `` The Red -LSB- One -RSB- ''  )  , La Furia Roja  (  `` The Red Fury ''  )  , La Furia Española  (  `` The Spanish Fury ''  )  or simply La Furia  (  `` The Fury ''  )  .

Furia is a Polish black metal band formed in 2003 in Katowice , with Michał `` Nihil '' Kuźniak on guitar and vocal , Kamil `` Sars '' Staszałek on bass , Przemysław `` Voldtekt '' on guitar and Grzegorz `` Namtar '' Kantor on drums .
Some members of Furia play in MasseMord , while the vocalist Nihil - who is also the lyricist - conducts the post-black project Morowe .
Additionally , Furia was a professor and director of film writing at the University of Southern California 's School of Cinema and Television .
